Description: Checkbox used to set whether to generate PLC code of Simulink mode. Linked to "Flag_Generate_PLC_app" in "inputfile.xlsx"

This light turns green if the reference source code file is present under the folder "ReferenceCFiles/originals". Additional fields MUST be added before code generation by right-clicking and selecting "Add Matlab Fields"
This light turns turn green if a Simulink model with the designated name is present in the folder "SimulinkModels" folder
This light indicates whether the App is ready for code generation. WARNING: remember to add matlab fields!
Creates a new empty Simulink model
Use to modify the SUBMODEL parameters of "inputfile.xlsx"
